reviewText: Consegna puntuale e gioia dei bimbi !

If you don't already have either of the SpongeBob movies; the original 2004 release and its prequel from 2015, Sponge Out of Water, this 2-in-1 DVD reissue is for you! If you wanted to get them on Blu-ray in this fashion, you're plumb out of luck, at least as of Fall 2016! What makes this review all the more exciting is season 10 of SpongeBob FINALLY started in October of 2016! This movie collection, like it is or separately, is a great way to ring it in! Whether it's Plankton finally stealing the Krabby Patty formula, or BurgerBeard stealing Plankton's thunder, these 2 instant classics are an awesome accompaniment to all the SpongeBob season sets, including to season 9, which won't be a DVD season set of its own until Christmastime next year, if not longer off, as a "guesstimation"! These 2 movies are definitely worth such a wait, even for SpongeBob's 11th season and 3rd theatrical movie, which won't be out for several years from now! "I'M READY!!!"
My child loves these films.  Spongebob's laugh drives me crazy.  Better value than purchasing films individually.
